1. *Želeo* je da se što pre vrati kući. (He wanted to return home as soon as possible.)

2. Ona je *želela* da se odseli u inostranstvo. (She wanted to move abroad.)

3. On *želi* da napusti zemlju. (He wants to leave the country.)

4. *Želeo* bih da dobijem bolju platu. (I would like to get a better salary.)

5. Ona *želeti* da se pridruži timu. (She wants to join the team.)

6. Oni su *želeli* da se druže sa nama. (They wanted to hang out with us.)